# UPLIFTLY - Project Requirements

> **AI-Powered Creator Platform for Video Content Analysis**

---

## ğŸ“‹ Project Overview

UPLIFTLY is an intelligent web platform designed to help content creators analyze, optimize, and improve their video content before publishing. By leveraging AI-powered analysis, creators can receive actionable insights and improvement suggestions to maximize audience engagement.

### Vision Statement
*Empower creators with AI-driven insights to produce better content faster.*

---

## ğŸ¯ MVP Features

### Core Features (Phase 1)
| Feature | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| User Authentication | Secure signup/login with JWT tokens | âœ… Implemented |
| User Dashboard | Personalized dashboard with analytics overview | âœ… Implemented |
| Video Upload | Upload videos for analysis | ğŸ”œ Coming Soon |
| AI Analysis Engine | Automated content analysis using AI/ML | ğŸ”œ Coming Soon |

### Planned Features (Phase 2)
- **Content Optimization Suggestions**: AI-generated recommendations for improving engagement
- **Thumbnail Analysis**: Evaluate and suggest better thumbnail options
- **Title/Description Optimization**: SEO-friendly suggestions
- **Audience Analytics**: Demographic and engagement predictions
- **Export Reports**: Downloadable analysis reports

